'''胞内体'''（{{lang-en|'''Endosome'''}}，又称'''内体'''）在[[细胞生物学|细胞生物学]]中指的是一种[[真核细胞|真核细胞]]中的膜结合[[细胞器|细胞器]]，属于一种[[囊泡|囊泡]]结构<ref>{{cite journal
| author = Ira Mellman
| title = ENDOCYTOSIS AND MOLECULAR SORTING
| journal = Annual Review of Cell and Developmental Biology
| volume = 12
| pages = 575–625
| pmid = 8970738
| doi = 10.1146/annurev.cellbio.12.1.575
|date=November 1996}}</ref>。作为细胞[[内吞作用|内吞作用]]中运载途径的一个区室，胞内体从[[细胞质膜|细胞质膜]]被传递到[[溶酶体|溶酶体]]被其[[降解|降解]]，或者再循环回到细胞质膜<ref>{{cite book
| title = 《细胞生物学》
| author = 王金发
| publisher = 科学出版社
| date = 2003年8月1日
| ISBN = 9787030114624
}}</ref>。一个成熟的内体直径大约500纳米<ref>{{cite journal
| author = Ian G. Ganley, Kate Carroll, Lenka Bittova, and Suzanne Pfeffer
| title = Rab9 GTPase Regulates Late Endosome Size and Requires Effector Interaction for Its Stability
| journal = Molecular Biology of the Cell
| volume = 15
| issue = 12
| pages = 5420–5430
| doi = 10.1091/mbc.E04-08-0747
| id = PMC532021 |date=December 2004}}</ref>。

== 类型 ==
胞内体可根据细胞内吞作用的不同时间阶段分为初级内体（{{lang|en|early endosome}}），次级内体（{{lang|en|late endosome}}），以及再循环内体（{{lang|en|recycling endosome}}），并可被如[[G蛋白|GTP结合蛋白]]rabs等蛋白标记而区分<ref>{{Cite journal
| author = H. Stenmark
| title = Rab GTPases as Coordinators of Vesicle Traffic
| journal = Nature Reviews Molecular Cell Biology
| volume = 10
| issue = 8
| pages = 513-525
| doi = 10.1038/nrm2728
| PMID = 19603039
|date=Aug 2009}}</ref>，并且此三种内体在形态上也有不同。一旦在[[内吞作用|内吞作用]]中的[[囊泡|囊泡]]被释放，它们首先与初级内体融合，之后再成长为次级内体并与[[溶酶体|溶酶体]]融合<ref>{{Cite journal
| author = C.E. Futter, A. Pearse, L.J. Hewlett, and C.R. Hopkins
| title = Multivesicular Endosomes Containing Internalized EGF-EGF Receptor Complexes Mature and then Fuse Directly with Lysosome
| url = https://archive.org/details/sim_journal-of-cell-biology_1996-03_132_6/page/1011
| journal = Journal of Cell Biology
| volume = 132
| issue = 6
| pages = 1011 - 1023
| doi = 10.1083/jcb.132.6.1011 
| PMID = 8601581
|date=March 1996}}</ref><ref>{{cite journal
| author = J.P. Luzio, B.A. Rous, N.A. Bright, P.R. Pryor, B.M. Mullock, and R.C. Piper
| title = Lysosome-Endosome Fusion and Lysosome Biogenesis
| journal = Journal of Cell Science
| volume = 113
| issue = 9
| pages = 1515 - 1524
| pmid = 10751143
| url = http://jcs.biologists.org/cgi/reprint/113/9/1515.pdf
|date=May 2000}}</ref>。

初级内体成长形成次级内体，随着其酸度通过V-ATpase的活动而增加<ref>{{Cite journal
| last1 = Lafourcade
| first1 = C.
| last2 = Sobo
| first2 = K.
| last3 = Kieffer-Jaquinod
| first3 = S.
| last4 = Garin
| first4 = J.
| last5 = van der Goot
| first5 = FG.
| title = Regulation of the V-ATPase along the Endocytic Pathway Occurs through Reversible Subunit Association and Membrane Localization
| journal = PLoS One
| volume = 3
| issue = 7
| pages = e2758
| doi = 10.1371/journal.pone.0002758
| PMID = 18648502
| url = http://www.plosone.org/article/info:doi/10.1371/journal.pone.0002758
|date=July 2008}}</ref>，并且大小通过融合同类型的内体成为更大的囊泡而增加<ref name="Rink-2005">{{Cite journal
| author = J. Rink, E. Chigo, Y. Kalaidzidis, and M. Zerial
| title = Rab Conversion as a Mechanism of Progression from Early to Late Endosomes
| journal = Cell
| volume = 122
| issue = 5
| pages = 735 - 749
| doi = 10.1016/j.cell.2005.06.043
| PMID = 16143105
| url = http://www.cell.com/abstract/S0092-8674%2805%2900697-5
|date=September 2005}}</ref>。次级内体或以为[[多泡体|多泡体]]（MVB）的形式呈现。最终，次级内体释放RAB5而获取RAB7，为其与溶酶体的融合做好准备<ref name="Rink-2005" />。 次级内体与溶酶体的融合是一个两种区室混合的过程，以结果来看，主要的生化特性也趋于原先二者的属性之间<ref name="endo-lysfus">{{Cite journal
| author = Barbara M. Mullock, Nicholas A. Bright, Clare W. Fearon, Sally R. Gray, and J. Paul Luzio
| title = Fusion of Lysosomes with Late Endosomes Produces a Hybrid Organelle of Intermediate Density and Is NSF Dependent 
| journal = Journal of Cell Biology
| volume = 140
| issue = 3
| pages = 591 - 601
| month = Feburary
| year = 1998
| doi = 10.1083/jcb.140.3.591
| PMID = 9456319
| url = http://jcb.rupress.org/content/140/3/591.full.pdf
}}</ref>。比如，溶酶体的密度大于次级内体，而融合后的密度介于二者之间。此后溶酶体重新聚合提高自身的密度，而在此之前可能有更多的次级内体与之融合。少数一些初级内体中的物质会直接再循环至细胞质膜<ref name="fastrecyc1">{{cite journal
| author = C.R. Hopkins, and I.S. Trowbridge
| title = Internalization and processing of transferrin and the transferrin receptor in human carcinoma A431 cells
| journal = Journal of Cell Biology
| volume = 97
| issue = 2
| pages = 508 - 521
| year = 1983
| doi = 10.1083/jcb.97.2.508
| pmid = 6309862
| url = http://jcb.rupress.org/content/97/2/508.full.pdf
}}</ref>，但多数还是通过再循环内体。

*'''初级内体'''：包含囊泡-小管网络，囊泡的直径可大至1微米，周围连接着直径大约50纳米的小管。标记物包括[[运铁蛋白|运铁蛋白]] RAB5，RAB4和它的运铁蛋白受体，以及EEA1。
*'''次级内体'''：也被称为多泡体，形态为球形，管状结构较少，主要包含密集的空腔状囊泡。标记物包括RAB7，RAB9，以及M6P受体<ref name="Russell-2006">{{Cite journal
| last1 = Russell
| first1 = MR.
| last2 = Nickerson
| first2 = DP.
